---
import PortalShell from "../layouts/PortalShell.astro";
---

<PortalShell activePage="guide" title="购买与交付说明" description="了解阿臭弟 AI 实战库的浏览、下单、微信联系和飞书知识库交付方式。">
  <header class="page-hero portal-container">
    <p class="eyebrow"><span></span> Guide</p>
    <div class="page-hero-row"><div><h1>购买与交付说明</h1><p>先看内容和Skill详情，确认需要后再添加微信沟通。</p></div></div>
  </header>
  <section class="portal-section guide-section">
    <div class="portal-container guide-layout">
      <aside class="guide-index" aria-label="指南目录">
        <strong>说明目录</strong>
        <a href="#read">阅读内容</a><a href="#skill">查看Skill</a><a href="#contact">微信联系</a><a href="#delivery">飞书交付</a>
      </aside>
      <div class="guide-content">
        <article id="read"><span class="guide-number">01</span><div><p class="section-kicker">Read</p><h2>阅读内容</h2><p>你可以先从首页和文章进入，了解我对电商 AI 生图、生视频和商业场景 Skill 的整理思路。文章内容后续会继续补充。</p></div></article>
        <article id="skill"><span class="guide-number">02</span><div><p class="section-kicker">Skill</p><h2>查看商业实战Skill</h2><p>AI实战库里会展示不同框架包。每个宝贝会先展示当前状态、简介、价格和说明，方便你判断是否适合自己的电商场景。</p></div></article>
        <article id="contact"><span class="guide-number">03</span><div><p class="section-kicker">Contact</p><h2>微信联系</h2><p>点击立即下单后会出现微信联系入口。添加时可以备注想了解的 Skill 名称，我会在微信里确认具体内容和购买方式。</p></div></article>
        <article id="delivery"><span class="guide-number">04</span><div><p class="section-kicker">Delivery</p><h2>飞书知识库交付</h2><p>确认后会发送对应飞书知识库和视频入口。知识库会按框架和场景持续整理，后续内容也会在对应空间里更新。</p></div></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PortalShell>
